{"id": "1472479741004091639", "channel_id": "1391701560496623688", "author_id": "846740886905683979", "author_name": "su0719", "content": "ログイン初めて7日目ですが、7章で勝つのが困難になってきてます。このパテの編成を変えた方がいいのか単純にレベル不足なのか教えて頂きたいです", "timestamp": "2026-02-15T06:28:47.606000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1472479741150756864", "filename": "IMG_0977.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1253854, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1391701560496623688/1472479741150756864/IMG_0977.png?ex=6a3438df&is=6a32e75f&hm=40c4d5f118207dffbf34019047cb5b4a5cf81460b17748db8bda93d74cfdc863&"}]}
